snippet.title: Soccer Stars Official Trailer
snippet.description:
SUBSCRIBE for more great videos!

Soccer Stars brings real-time multiplayer soccer to iOS and Android! Challenge players from around the world or take on your friends! 

Click here to download on iOS: http://mcgam.es/SSiosYT
Click here to download on Android: http://mcgam.es/SSandYT
